text: Kalkot is a tehsil of Upper Dir District, Khyber Pakhtunkhwa. It is located in the northern most point in Pakistan's Pakhtunkhwa. Muhammad Zada is the current tehsildar and he is from the Pakistan Muslim League party. == References == Category:Tehsils of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Category:Upper Dir District
title: Kalkot Tehsil
